    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在巨大的飞艇上，居住着人类的最后幸存者，他们是仍在地球上肆虐的格雷尔战争的幸存者。  部署时间行者机甲至地面，这些机甲具备在战斗中操控时间的能力，以保护你的搜救队伍。  从废墟般的地面收集装备、补给和幸存者。  升级、改进，或许有一天，你能找到逆转末日的关键。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特点</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将机甲送回过去，创建重复的防御者</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特的战斗中机甲动作（移动和战斗能力）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >机甲升级和自定义</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特的机甲飞行员</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可升级的炮塔</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支援炮塔、无人机等</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可破坏的环境</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动态战场，包括地形高度、多条路径等</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>回到过去，重新思考。</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >面对压倒性的蜂群，将你的机甲送回过去以扭转局势。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037800/extras/3a437ab03bcabca6f3b3966357cff894.poster.avif?t=1771863197\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037800/extras/3a437ab03bcabca6f3b3966357cff894.webm?t=1771863197\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037800/extras/3a437ab03bcabca6f3b3966357cff894.mp4?t=1771863197\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当你将机甲送回过去时，你有机会再次挑战该关卡，但这次你将拥有一台相同的机甲。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你需要更多帮助，可以再将另一台机甲送回同一点。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>经典塔防游戏玩法</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在探索失落地球废墟的过程中，保护你的救援小队免受克雷尔的袭击。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >部署炮塔并调整机甲位置，以抵御蜂拥而至的敌军。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当空间有限时，升级防御系统以增强攻击力。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>塔防策略游戏</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在战斗中重新部署机甲以获得战略优势。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037800/extras/8ac864dc2a396b3e71c5bf14f24dc9d7.poster.avif?t=1771863197\" width=730 height=396 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037800/extras/8ac864dc2a396b3e71c5bf14f24dc9d7.webm?t=1771863197\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037800/extras/8ac864dc2a396b3e71c5bf14f24dc9d7.mp4?t=1771863197\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >近战型机甲可用于防御道路并减缓与之交战的敌军。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >配备跳跃喷射器的机甲可快速穿越战场，并跳跃至高处以提升视野范围。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037800/extras/1d1fc801f1d27b215bdc6beee6b31986.poster.avif?t=1771863197\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037800/extras/1d1fc801f1d27b215bdc6beee6b31986.webm?t=1771863197\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037800/extras/1d1fc801f1d27b215bdc6beee6b31986.mp4?t=1771863197\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>机械能力</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >机甲的装备配置赋予其被动和主动战斗能力。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用重力锤摧毁建筑物，为你的防御工事腾出更多空间。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037800/extras/fd4f35304ade3fecb421af03337927c9.poster.avif?t=1771863197\" width=800 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037800/extras/fd4f35304ade3fecb421af03337927c9.webm?t=1771863197\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037800/extras/fd4f35304ade3fecb421af03337927c9.mp4?t=1771863197\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >搭建一个平台，然后利用机甲的跳跃喷射器为其争取制高点。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在紧急情况下，使用自动炮的“子弹风暴”技能，释放密集的弹雨。</p></li></ul>",
